    type: string
    default: a 3-month software release timeline
---
Create a Gantt chart or project timeline showing tasks, durations, dependencies, and milestones along a horizontal time axis. Use colored bars for different task categories and diamond markers for milestones. Show the critical path. The subject of this diagram is: {{subject}}.
